            "as_at_date": "07/03/2017"
          },
          {
            "rule_number": "2.7",
            "summary": "1. (1) Before deciding whether a person (P) is fit and proper, a firm must take reasonable steps to obtain appropriate references covering the past 6 years from the following:",
