            "rule_number": "2.9",
            "summary": "In deciding whether a person (P) is fit and proper in connection with a PRA senior management approval application or on appointment as a notified non-executive director or _credit union non-exe",
            "as_at_date": "10/12/2018"
          },
          {
            "rule_number": "2.10",
            "summary": "If a firm previously obtained the information in 2.7 to [2.9](/pra-rules/fitness-and-propriety#f6ba3b8ec7ca4e0e9627975a6b1e",
            "as_at_date": "07/03/2017"
